name: The Apple tree
description:
I have never really felt inspired to sell my art.
My philosophy on what, why and value are not un-common, or eureka. 
Its been challenging lately,
and my mind has been distracted.
I did not want to share, demanding my slice!
kinda bondage of self thing. Sometimes I too need reminding of I'm spelling  gratatude wrong from the moment artistic wonder went 3 dimensional. not from this computer, but from cave art had it's first clockwork orange"
 sorry tilt brush community.

So apart from the odd few, I hope i can inspire a drawing to be mixed. And thank you so much if you do use this image in any way. @tmm2@sj2020
